    },
    {
      "content": "This article is an end-to-end tutorial of the scenarios and capabilities of Azure Data Catalog public preview.",
      "pos": [
        507,
        617
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Once you sign up for the preview, you can follow these steps to create a Data Catalog, and register, annotate, and discover data sources.",
