        618,
        755
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Tutorial prerequisites",
      "pos": [
        760,
        782
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Before you begin this tutorial you must have the following:",
      "pos": [
        784,
        843
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>An Azure subscription<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> -  If you don't have a subscription, you can create a free trial account in just a couple of minutes.",
      "pos": [
        849,
        976
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Free Trial<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/pricing/free-trial/)</ept> article for details.",
      "pos": [
        977,
        1066
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1071,
        1240
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Active Directory<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> -  Azure Data Catalog uses <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Azure Active Directory<ept id=\"p2\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/services/active-directory/)</ept> for identity and access management."
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Data sources<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> - Azure Data Catalog provides capabilities for data source discovery, and to proceed with the tutorial you must have access to one or more data sources.",
      "pos": [
        1245,
        1414
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The tutorial is written using the Adventure Works sample databases, but you can use any supported data source if you would prefer to work with data that is familiar and relevant to your role.",
      "pos": [
        1415,
        1606
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Exercise 1: Install Adventure Works sample database",
      "pos": [
        1611,
        1662
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this exercise, you install the Adventure Works sample for SQL Server Database Engine, and SQL Server Analysis Services Multidimensional.",
      "pos": [
        1664,
        1803
      ]
    },
    {
