    {
      "content": "Exercise 3: Discovering Registered Data Assets",
      "pos": [
        5211,
        5257
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this exercise you will use the Azure Data Catalog portal to discover registered data assets and view their metadata.",
      "pos": [
        5259,
        5378
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Data Catalog provides multiple tools for discovering data assets, including simple keyword search, interactive filters, and an advanced search syntax for “power” users.",
      "pos": [
        5379,
        5553
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Here’s how you discover registered data assets",
      "pos": [
        5559,
        5605
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> has a simple but powerful search syntax that enables you to easily build queries that return the data the users need.",
      "pos": [
        5607,
        5747
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For details about <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, see Search syntax reference.",
      "pos": [
        5748,
        5818
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        5820,
        5876
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> has the following search options:"
    },
    {
      "content": "Keyword search",
      "pos": [
        5880,
        5894
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Filter",
      "pos": [
        5897,
        5903
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Advanced search",
      "pos": [
        5906,
        5921
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can also refine what data assets to view.",
      "pos": [
        5923,
        5968
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> has the following view options:",
      "pos": [
        5969,
        6023
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "View properties",
      "pos": [
        6027,
        6042
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "View columns",
      "pos": [
        6045,
        6057
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "View preview",
      "pos": [
        6060,
        6072
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For this example, you will use a keyword search.",
      "pos": [
        6074,
        6122
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> search has several query techniques.",
      "pos": [
        6123,
        6182
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This example will use a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Grouping<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> search query.",
      "pos": [
        6183,
        6233
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Query Techniques",
      "pos": [
        6237,
        6253
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Technique",
      "pos": [
        6274,
        6283
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use",
      "pos": [
        6299,
        6302
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Example",
      "pos": [
        6318,
        6325
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Property Scoping",
      "pos": [
        6347,
        6363
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Only return data sources where the search term is matched in the specified property",
      "pos": [
        6372,
        6455
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "name:product",
      "pos": [
        6464,
        6476
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Logical Operators",
      "pos": [
        6494,
        6511
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Broaden or narrow a search using Boolean operations, as described in the Boolean Operators section on this page",
      "pos": [
        6520,
        6631
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "finance NOT corporate",
      "pos": [
        6640,
        6661
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Grouping with Parenthesis",
      "pos": [
        6679,
        6704
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use parentheses to group parts of the query to achieve logical isolation, especially in conjunction with Boolean operators",
      "pos": [
        6713,
        6835
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "name:product AND (tags:illustration OR tags:photo)",
      "pos": [
        6844,
        6894
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Comparison Operators",
      "pos": [
        6912,
        6932
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use comparisons other than equality for properties that have numeric and date data types",
      "pos": [
        6941,
        7029
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "creationTime:&amp;gt;11/05/14",
      "pos": [
        7038,
        7063
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7083,
        7219
      ],
      "content": "In this example, you do a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Grouping<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> search for data assets where name equals product and tags equal illustration or tags equal photo."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7225,
        7268
      ],
      "content": "Log into the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> portal."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7273,
        7292
      ],
      "content": "Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Discover<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7297,
        7377
      ],
      "content": "In <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Search<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> box, enter a <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Grouping<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> query: (tags:description OR tags:photo)."
    },
    {
      "content": "Click the search icon, or press Enter.",
      "pos": [
        7382,
        7420
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> will display data assets for this search query.",
      "pos": [
        7421,
        7491
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "![search][8]",
      "pos": [
        7497,
        7509
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7511,
        7632
      ],
      "content": "In this exercise you used the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> portal to discover and view data assets registered with the catalog."
    },
    {
      "content": "Exercise 4: Annotating registered data sources",
      "pos": [
        7637,
        7683
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this exercise you will use the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> portal to annotate data assets that have been previously registered in the catalog.",
      "pos": [
        7685,
        7825
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The annotations you provide will supplement and enhance the structural metadata extracted from the data source during registration and will make the data assets even easier to discover and understand.",
      "pos": [
        7826,
        8026
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Because each <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> user can provide his own annotations, it’s easy for every user with a perspective on the data to share it.",
      "pos": [
        8027,
        8163
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Here’s how you annotate data assets",
      "pos": [
        8169,
        8204
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        8210,
        8253
      ],
      "content": "Log into the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> portal."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        8258,
        8277
      ],
      "content": "Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Discover<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "content": "Choose one or more <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Data Assets<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        8282,
        8317
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this example, choose <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>ProductPhoto<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, and enter “Product photos for marketing materials.”",
      "pos": [
        8318,
        8411
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Enter a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Description<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> that will help other discover and understand why and how to use the selected data asset.",
      "pos": [
        8416,
        8528
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, enter “Product images”.",
      "pos": [
        8529,
        8565
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can also add more tags, and view columns.",
      "pos": [
        8566,
        8611
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Now you can try searching and filtering to discover data assets using the descriptive metadata you’ve added to the catalog.",
      "pos": [
        8616,
        8739
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "![annotate][9]",
      "pos": [
        8745,
        8759
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this exercise you added descriptive information to registered data assets so that catalog users can discover data source using terms they understand.",
      "pos": [
