        10041
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Exercise: Connecting to Data Sources",
      "pos": [
        10042,
        10078
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this exercise you will use the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Azure Data Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> portal to connect to data sources using Microsoft Excel.",
      "pos": [
        10079,
        10192
      ]
